Is this Bakuchiol face toner safe for sensitive skin? Yes! We created this Bakuchiol face toner for everyone to enjoy. We use clean, effective ingredients that will never irritate your skin – we promise. Is this Bakuchiol face toner easy to use? It doesn’t get any easier than this! Simply spritz this Bakuchiol toner after cleansing your cute face, and voilà! You can also apply this toner with a reusable cotton pad, if that’s more your jam. How strong is the scent of this Bakuchiol face toner? Not strong. You’ll enjoy a refreshing scent upon application that dissipates within a few seconds.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars All in one
reviews.reviewText: Im obsessed with the fact that this toner contains all of the most important ingredients in skin care & all of the ingredients I’ve been wanting to add to my routine!!! Retinol, (or the natural version Bakuchiol,) Niacinamide, Hyaluronic acid & a lot more! Definitely check out the ingredient list. I love that it’s all in one.I’ve been wanting to go more natural, clean, non toxic & chemical free so I’ve loved finally getting to try bakuchiol, which is the the natural, plant based version retinol, but is just as powerful. Another thing I appreciate is that this toner is good for acne prone skin & that it’s alcohol free. Also the fact that it’s pore refining, because that’s something that’s important for me to have in a toner.It’s helped my redness and break outs, my skin has looked a lot more clear since I’ve started using it. It helps my pores appear smaller while making my face feel smoother. Definitely on my must have list

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great, natural ingredient toner
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Let me start off by saying, this toner is hydrating & does not strip your face by any means. It’s perfect for those with sensitive skin, as it doesn’t contain any harmful ingredients and is light on the skin. An all natural scent, with amazing ingredients you can read! I’ve been using this alongside their moisturizer & it’s been the perfect duo in bringing my dry skin back to life! The only con is the sprayer has the product come out FAST, I do wish it was more of a mist than a stream. But if you hold it far enough back, you can avoid that. Isn’t a big deal because I love the toner so much! Add this one into your routine!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works magic without the photosensitivity!
reviews.reviewText: I recently turned 35 and started noticing enlarged pores and I tried out this product because it was plantbased and cruelty free. I never heard of Bakuchiol so I was curious what benefits it has in store for my skin! I began using daily for 3 weeks and noticed visibly brighter skin, tighter and glowing as well! After a long day out in the sun I spray this on my face and follow with the facial moisturizer cream and the redness goes away and skin is glowing and being nourished as well! Definitely try this out!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better Alternative for Retinol
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been using this product for about three weeks and have genuinely loved it. Retinol makes my skin super dry and patchy, but I didn’t experience that with this natural alternative. I didn’t have a toner in my current face routine and I’ve enjoyed adding this in a few times a week. As always, I recommend doing a patch test before use! Overall, I like this product and it has not caused any problems. I will say my face feels better and overall appearance has improved as well. My only suggestion for the future would be a sprayer that has a finer mist!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Goes on like lotion
reviews.reviewText: I have tried so many toners that leave my skin feeling super dry and even causes my face to peel. But this! This goes on so smooth and feels like lotion. It has such a light smell and actually leaves me skin feeling moisturized. I have put this on some days and didn’t even add my moisturizer and my face was still as hydrated as it would be with a moisturizer. I definitely recommend this if you’re looking for a lightweight toner!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better than other toners I’ve bought!
reviews.reviewText: I’ve tried several toners over the years and even micellar water to clean my face. I like the way this toner cleans dirt off my face while also making my pours appear smaller. My face gets oily easily and breaks out and also gets clogged with dirt a lot throughout the day. This helps clean all that off and I also use it to take my makeup off at night, it leaves my face feeling soft. Will definitely buy again. Also has a fruity scent to it that smells great.
